snippet.title: Super Time Force Ultra - PlayStation Experience Trailer | PS4, PS Vita
snippet.description:
Super Time Force Ultra is coming to PlayStation 4 and PlayStation VITA! 

For more info, head to http://www.supertimeforce 

SUPER TIME FORCE ULTRA is a crazy romp through the space-time continuum. Jump in and out of 6 unique time periods with a ton of different modes, playable characters and collectibles! Grab the steering wheel of time and use it to your advantage, timing out and rejoining the action alongside your past selves in 'single player co-op'. 

May contain content inappropriate for children, visit www.esrb.org for rating information

Copyright 2014 Capybara Games Inc.
